<section class="subs section" aria-labelledby="subs-heading">
	<div class="container">
		<p class="eyebrow">Built for subs</p>
		<h2 id="subs-heading" class="subs__heading">
			We come from blue-collar technology, not social networks and dating apps.
		</h2>
		<p class="subs__body">
			Soyer is built by people who know the tech world would rather build the
			sexy app than serve the trades. We've watched truckers sit in a lot at 3am
			— a country away from home, wrecked from a three-day haul — fighting with
			an app just to prove they finished the run. So we built the tech those
			drivers actually needed, for the drivers.
		</p>
		<p class="subs__body">
			Now we've watched skilled crews do the work, then fight for weeks to
			collect money they earned honestly. So we're building the tech subs need —
			that's Soyer.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.subs__heading {
		font-size: clamp(1.625rem, 4.5vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
		line-height: 1.15;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		max-width: 24ch;
	}

	.subs__body {
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		max-width: 62ch;
	}
</style>
